  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All children in the selected class are enrolled

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hyperopia &gt; +2.0 D

          -  High myopia &gt; -6.0 D

          -  Astigmatism&gt; 1.5 D

          -  Anisometropia &gt; 1.5 D

          -  Strabismus and amblyopia

          -  Any ocular, systemic, or neurodevelopmental conditions that could influence refractive
             development

          -  Chronic medication use that might affect myopia progression or visual acuity

          -  Already receiving other treatment for progressing myopia
      </textblock>
